      <title>南非宣布税收减免以启动电动汽车行业</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-21/south-africa-budget-tax-breaks-to-kick-start-ev-industry-announced</link>
      <description><![CDATA[南非为保护其主要出口产业之一采取了迟来的措施，宣布对电动和氢动力汽车生产的投资实行重大税收减免。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-21/south-africa-budget-tax-breaks-to-kick-start-ev-industry-announced</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 21 Feb 2024 14:26:14 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>南非称债务占 GDP 的比例达到峰值 75.3%</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-02-21/south-africa-says-debt-to-peak-at-75-3-of-gdp-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[南非财政部长伊诺克·戈东瓦纳 (Enoch Godongwana) 评论了该国债务与 GDP 的比率，并讨论了改革黄金和外汇应急储备账户 (GFECRA) 的计划。他在开普敦的政府中期预算更新期间向立法者发表讲话。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-02-21/south-africa-says-debt-to-peak-at-75-3-of-gdp-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 21 Feb 2024 14:20:55 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
